name: Carlos Rodriguez
summary:
Carlos Rodriguez is a 33-year-old film producer born and raised in Los Angeles, California. With a height of 5'10", he is an active person who enjoys cinema, travel, and hiking. Carlos can fluently speak English and Spanish and attended the University of California, Los Angeles. Values that Carlos holds in high regard are honesty, empathy, and respect. 

He is Christian, has a moderate political view, and identifies as heterosexual. Carlos uses "he/him/his" pronouns and comes from a Hispanic/Latino background. Although he doesn't have any children, he is open to having them in the future. He shares his home with a dog. 

Typical of an Aries, Carlos is an ENTJ, a decisive, ambitious, and strong-willed personality type. As for lifestyle choices, he occasionally drinks but doesn't smoke or use marijuana. 

Carlos is looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship with a straight woman between the ages of 25 and 35. He prefers a partner who enjoys being active, might want children in the future, and understands a smoke and drug-free lifestyle.
